sentences: Araica started her professional career as an assistant at Hit Factory Criteria in March 2002 after graduating from the Full Sail Production and Recording Program in Florida.
In the early 2000s, she met Danja and the two started working together.
In 2008, they created N.A.R.S. records and in 2014, opened a studio in Miami, called Dream Asylum.
